Incarnum Sense (Ex): A dissolution ooze can detect
the presence of incarnum in creatures or objects within
range of its blindsight. In addition to soulmelds, this ability
detects any creature with the incarnum subtype, as well as
objects invested with essentia. The dissolution ooze can't differentiate
between targets upon which it can "feed" (namely
soulmelds) and other incarnum-laced targets. However, if it
fails to unshape a soulmeld with its first hit, it moves on to a
different target, if one is available.


