Create Spawn (Su): Any humanoid that has an essentia
pool and is slain by an incarnum wraith becomes a new
incarnum wraith in 1d4 rounds. Its body remains intact
and inanimate, but its spirit is torn free from its corpse and
transformed. Such spawn are under the command of the
incarnum wraith that created them and remain enslaved
until its death. They do not possess any of the abilities they
had in life.
A humanoid that does not have an essentia pool is merely
dead if slain by an incarnum wraith. It does not become a
new incarnum wraith.
